#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.geometric"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from the geometric distribution."
msgstr "从几何分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:3 of
msgid ""
"Bernoulli trials are experiments with one of two outcomes: success or "
"failure (an example of such an experiment is flipping a coin).  The "
"geometric distribution models the number of trials that must be run in "
"order to achieve success.  It is therefore supported on the positive "
"integers, ``k = 1, 2, ...``."
msgstr ""
"伯努利试验是只有两种结果的实验：成功或失败（例如抛硬币）。几何分布模拟了"
"为了获得成功所需进行的试验次数。因此它支持正整数，``k = 1, 2, ...``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:9 of
msgid "The probability mass function of the geometric distribution is"
msgstr "几何分布的概率质量函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:11 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"f(k) = (1 - p)^{k - 1} p\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:13 of
msgid "where `p` is the probability of success of an individual trial."
msgstr "其中 `p` 是单次试验成功的概率。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:15 of
msgid "The probability of success of an individual trial."
msgstr "单次试验成功的概率。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:17 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``p`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``mt.array(p).size`` samples "
"are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。"
"如果 size 是 ``None``（默认），当 ``p`` 是标量时返回单个值。否则抽取 ``mt"
".array(p).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:22 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:24 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:26 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:29 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized geometric distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的几何分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:33 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:34 of
msgid ""
"Draw ten thousand values from the geometric distribution, with the "
"probability of an individual success equal to 0.35:"
msgstr "从几何分布中抽取一万个值，单次成功的概率为 0.35："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.geometric.geometric:41 of
msgid "How many trials succeeded after a single run?"
msgstr "一次运行后有多少次试验成功？"

